CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 7, 1964, pg. 7, reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Charles Golphin...recently married"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of groom Charles Golphin wearing bow tie and jacket with satin lapels, bride wearing gown with lace overlay and mid length veil, and another man, standing behind three tiered wedding cake in interior with twisted crepe paper streamers
